arvind krishna  wikipedia arvind krishna from wikipedia the free encyclopedia   redirected from aravind krishna jump to navigation search this article is about the cinematographer for the actor see arvind krishna actor arvind krishna born arvind krishna new delhi other names aravind krishna occupation cinematographer years active present spouses anupama arvind arvind krishna is an indian cinematographer who has worked in the indian film and television industry contents  early life  marriage  career  filmography  as producer  as actor  references  external links early lifeedit born in new delhi on the th of may arvind krishna has spent his childhood traversing between chennai and delhi educated in vidya mandirmylapore he holds a professional graduate degree in visual communication from loyola college chennai his father a producer was one of the first to produce a tv series for doordarshan called adade manohar skrishnan  arvinds father owned a film lab called “aarkay home movies” and a production company called “ark media” arvind was inspired by his father and thus chose to pursue a career in the films and television medium marriageedit he is married to anupama arvind careeredit cinematography his first stint was with pcsreeram with whom he interned for six years in this role he assisted him in the cinematography department and worked on several prestigious ad campaigns television commercials and feature films he then moved to work independently as a cinematographer subsequently he met film director selvaraghavan and was his chief camera person for kadhal kondein g rainbow colony and pudhupettai gautham menon noted producer and director collaborated with arvind krishna on “pachaikili muthucharam” arvind has also worked with veteran pvasu for the film kuselan alvijay and arvind worked together on poi solla porom a remake of “khosla ka ghosla“ some of the creative influences for arvind’s work as a cinematographer is the works of vilmos zsigmond janusz kamiński and ashok mehta production in  he relaunched “ark media” and produced for star vijay a tv series called “dharmayutham” an acclaimed first of its kind legal drama for this production he was the creative head cum producer the serial has been directed by alabanindranit stars raja krishnamoorthyabbas evam’s karthik kumaranuja iyerseason one has just seen its completion and season two is likely to kick off soon this production was telecasted for  months spanning  episodes ark media is currently in the preproduction phase for a few more tv series in different genres acting arvind krishna has dabbled in acting and was featured in padmashri kamal hassans police story “kurudhipunal “ in a much appreciated role as dhanush he also starred in rajeev menon’s “kandukonden kandukonden” as protagonist’s best friend in addition he did a cameo appearance in “poi solla poram” and “theeratha vilayatu pillai” filmographyedit thulluvadho ilamai  kaadhal kondein  g rainbow colony  chakram  telugu film pudhupettai  pachaikili muthucharam  kuselan  poi solla porom  vaamanan 9 theeradha vilaiyattu pillai  baava telugu thank you  malayalam film gods own country malayalam film peruchazhi malayalam film kanithan  nibunan  nenjam marappathillai  as produceredit dharmayutham star vijay  season one as actoredit kurudhipunal 99 dhanush kandukondain kandukondain  poi solla porom  police officer theeradha vilaiyattu pillai  doctor its my love story  gods own country  peruchazhi  guest appearance referencesedit we are creative gamblers chennai india the hindu  httpwwwhinducomthehindumpstories9htm retrieved 9 dhanush under white elephants oneindia httpentertainmentoneindiaintamiltopstoriesdhanushwhiteelephantshtml retrieved 9 aravind krishna and selvaraghavan part ways cinesouthcom httpwwwcinesouthcommasalahotnewsnewshtml retrieved 9 dharmayutham on vijay tv promises to be a refreshing change chennai online httpchennaionlinecommoviespreviewdharmayuthamonvijaytvpromisestobearefreshingchangecol retrieved  novembe